649
00:38:30,170 --> 00:38:35,370
[Eum Hyeok Jin: in the previous shoot,
he only came to my room once.]

650
00:38:35,370 --> 00:38:38,880
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I was always the one looking for him.]

651
00:38:38,880 --> 00:38:43,800
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
But now, he comes to our room often.]

652
00:38:46,210 --> 00:38:49,160
[Su Min is proactive in pursuing Sun Wook]

653
00:38:49,160 --> 00:38:52,500
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I feel hurt.]

654
00:38:56,430 --> 00:38:58,610
[Kim Han Gyeol: Hello.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Morning.]

655
00:38:58,610 --> 00:39:00,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You haven't eaten, right?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: No.]

656
00:39:00,440 --> 00:39:01,800
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Have that.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Is this rice?]

657
00:39:01,800 --> 00:39:03,530
[Lee Hyun Jun: Toast.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I made it.]

658
00:39:03,530 --> 00:39:06,450
[Kim Han Gyeol: Really? Oh, thank you.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Eat up.]

659
00:39:06,450 --> 00:39:08,360
[Kim Han Gyeol: Wow, you're a good cook.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: No, no.]

660
00:39:08,360 --> 00:39:10,000
[Kim Han Gyeol: When did you make this?]

661
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:12,640
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
What time was it? Did I get up at 7 AM?]

662
00:39:12,640 --> 00:39:14,610
[Lee Hyun Jun: 8 AM?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I couldn't sleep.]

663
00:39:14,610 --> 00:39:16,650
[Lee Hyun Jun: 8:30 AM?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I got up around 7 AM.]

664
00:39:16,650 --> 00:39:20,060
[Kim Han Gyeol: Thank you so much.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: No problem. Enjoy.]

665
00:39:25,120 --> 00:39:27,000
[Takes a big bite]

666
00:39:28,300 --> 00:39:30,110
[Happy]

667
00:39:35,060 --> 00:39:36,800
[Park Jae Ha: Who wants to make snowmen?]

668
00:39:36,800 --> 00:39:38,440
[Park Jae Ha: It's me.]

669
00:39:38,500 --> 00:39:40,630
Really? You'll freeze your hands off.

670
00:39:47,580 --> 00:39:50,930
[Park Jae Ha: Did you add the eyes?]
[Kim Sun Wook: It doesn't stick. Just a scarf.]

671
00:39:51,280 --> 00:39:52,390
[Swish]

672
00:39:53,180 --> 00:39:55,040
[Joyful]

673
00:39:59,550 --> 00:40:03,780
[They're all smiles thanks to the first snow]

674
00:40:05,350 --> 00:40:07,830
[Park Jae Ha: Who wants to find its eyes with me?]

675
00:40:07,830 --> 00:40:09,340
[Park Jae Ha: The snowman's eyes.]

676
00:40:14,010 --> 00:40:15,460
[Heave-ho]

677
00:40:15,770 --> 00:40:18,270
[Lee Hyeok Jin: That tree doesn't move at all.]

678
00:40:18,470 --> 00:40:20,350
[Shaking]

679
00:40:21,020 --> 00:40:22,680
[Laughing]

680
00:40:28,200 --> 00:40:30,520
[Eum Hyeok Jin: He has really bad aim.]

681
00:40:30,520 --> 00:40:32,890
[Lee Hyun Jun: Even when the target's still.]

682
00:40:32,890 --> 00:40:35,680
[Kim Su Min: He shouldn't do sports.]

683
00:40:37,130 --> 00:40:39,190
[Staring]

684
00:40:39,780 --> 00:40:42,710
[Hyung, come out!] [Me?]

685
00:40:45,810 --> 00:40:47,940
[(Gets up)]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Challenging me, huh?]

686
00:40:51,860 --> 00:40:53,290
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm burning up.]

687
00:40:53,290 --> 00:40:55,200
[Kim Sun Wook: It's been a while.]

688
00:40:56,300 --> 00:40:57,060
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Challenging me?]

689
00:40:57,060 --> 00:40:58,940
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Let's have a snow fight.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You sure?]

690
00:40:58,940 --> 00:41:00,650
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
Let's have snow... a snow fight.]

691
00:41:00,650 --> 00:41:02,530
You sure you want a snow fight?

692
00:41:02,530 --> 00:41:02,670
You don't...

693
00:41:02,670 --> 00:41:04,870
[Park Jae Ha: Go see the snowman we made.]

694
00:41:04,870 --> 00:41:05,510
[Park Jae Ha: It's cute.]

695
00:41:05,510 --> 00:41:08,900
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Not an athletic bone in you.]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: No, I played volleyball.]

696
00:41:08,900 --> 00:41:10,740
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
No way. You missed all your shots.]

697
00:41:12,070 --> 00:41:14,210
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I haven't touched snow
with my bare hands in a long time.]

698
00:41:16,020 --> 00:41:17,780
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Gosh, you have really bad aim.]

699
00:41:26,450 --> 00:41:28,660
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Ah, it's so cold.]

700
00:41:34,820 --> 00:41:36,950
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's so cold.]

701
00:41:36,950 --> 00:41:38,700
[Park Jae Ha: He's good at dodging.]

702
00:41:38,700 --> 00:41:42,300
[Kim Sun Wook: One can't aim, and one can dodge.]

703
00:41:42,300 --> 00:41:44,050
[Park Jae Ha: What a dream combo.]

704
00:41:44,050 --> 00:41:46,150
[Park Jae Ha:
The one who can't aim and the one who dodges.]

705
00:41:59,630 --> 00:42:02,030
[Staring]

706
00:42:05,860 --> 00:42:09,430
[Hyeong Jun goes into his room alone]

707
00:42:23,020 --> 00:42:25,240
[A glance]

708
00:42:41,850 --> 00:42:44,040
[Kim Sun Wook: What are you doing?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Hmm?]

709
00:42:44,040 --> 00:42:45,020
[Kim Sun Wook: What are you doing?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Nothing.]

710
00:42:45,020 --> 00:42:46,660
[Kim Sun Wook: Need a rest?]

711
00:42:46,660 --> 00:42:48,890
[Lee Hyeong Jun: There's nothing to do.]

712
00:42:51,710 --> 00:42:54,490
[Lee Hyeong Jun: What's wrong?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Go kick the snowman down.]

713
00:42:54,490 --> 00:42:58,250
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I can't be bothered.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah?]

714
00:43:08,430 --> 00:43:11,540
[Uneasy]

715
00:43:13,270 --> 00:43:15,860
[Kim Su Min: Whose bed is this?]
[Kim Sun Wook: It's Hyeok Jin's.]

716
00:43:15,860 --> 00:43:18,510
[Lee Hyeong Jun: He sleeps in the middle.]

717
00:43:18,510 --> 00:43:20,100
[Kim Su Min:
I should get permission to sit on others' beds.]

718
00:43:20,100 --> 00:43:21,030
[Lee Hyeong Jun: It's OK.]

719
00:43:21,030 --> 00:43:22,880
[Kim Sun Wook: It's OK. They're all our beds.]

720
00:43:26,020 --> 00:43:27,350
[Pauses]

721
00:43:29,330 --> 00:43:31,380
[Staring]

722
00:43:33,070 --> 00:43:35,720
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Sigh...]

723
00:43:35,720 --> 00:43:39,010
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I can't even go outside.]
[Kim Su Min: Why?]

724
00:43:39,010 --> 00:43:40,680
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Jae Ha.]

725
00:43:43,020 --> 00:43:45,660
[Kim Sun Wook: Haven't you talked yet?]

726
00:43:45,660 --> 00:43:48,250
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I haven't said a word to him.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Really?]

727
00:43:48,250 --> 00:43:50,020
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yesterday too.]

728
00:43:55,350 --> 00:44:00,310
[Kim Su Min: A lot on your mind?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: No, quite the opposite.]

729
00:44:03,530 --> 00:44:04,890
[Lee Hyeong Jun: A lot on your mind?]
[Kim Su Min: Hmm?]

730
00:44:04,890 --> 00:44:07,030
[Lee Hyeong Jun: A lot on your mind?]
[Kim Su Min: Not really.]

731
00:44:07,030 --> 00:44:09,150
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Seems like it.]

732
00:44:10,890 --> 00:44:13,040
[Kim Su Min: You have a lot on your mind, right?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Me?]

733
00:44:13,040 --> 00:44:14,080
[Kim Su Min: Yeah.]

734
00:44:15,500 --> 00:44:17,070
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Sort of.]

735
00:44:18,230 --> 00:44:21,220
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I can't say I don't.]

736
00:44:24,080 --> 00:44:25,880
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I heard you called each other.]

737
00:44:29,690 --> 00:44:31,350
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Look at your face!]

738
00:44:31,350 --> 00:44:32,840
[Kim Su Min: You guys share everything, huh?]

739
00:44:32,840 --> 00:44:36,310
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
Oh? It's true? I was just feeling you out.]

740
00:44:36,310 --> 00:44:39,830
[Kim Su Min: You're so good at this.]

741
00:44:42,540 --> 00:44:44,720
[Kim Su Min: We should have a drink.]

742
00:44:44,720 --> 00:44:46,430
[Lee Hyeong Jun: With me?]
[Kim Su Min: Yeah.]

743
00:44:46,430 --> 00:44:49,070
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Sounds good. Let's drink.]
[Kim Su Min: Now?]

744
00:44:49,070 --> 00:44:52,330
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Not now.]
[Kim Su Min: Yeah.]

745
00:44:57,070 --> 00:45:00,390
[Park Jae Ha: I have a lot to tell Hyeong Jun.]

746
00:45:00,640 --> 00:45:03,880
[Park Jae Ha:
When Hyeong Jun arrived on the first day,]

747
00:45:03,880 --> 00:45:06,610
[Park Jae Ha: I wanted to talk to him then.]

748
00:45:06,610 --> 00:45:08,620
[Park Jae Ha: Have an honest talk. But it...]

749
00:45:08,620 --> 00:45:10,640
[Park Jae Ha: It seemed inappropriate.]

750
00:45:10,640 --> 00:45:14,860
[Park Jae Ha: When there's a chance,
I want to talk to Hyeong Jun alone.]

751
00:45:14,860 --> 00:45:18,090
[Park Jae Ha: So I've been looking for a chance.]

752
00:45:23,330 --> 00:45:24,770
[Park Jae Ha: Are you going to rest?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Hmm?]

753
00:45:24,770 --> 00:45:26,690
[Park Jae Ha: Are you going to rest?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah.]

754
00:45:32,340 --> 00:45:33,650
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why are you here?]
[Park Jae Ha: Hmm?]

755
00:45:33,650 --> 00:45:35,340
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why are you here?]

756
00:45:38,290 --> 00:45:41,340
[Park Jae Ha:
We just ate. Want to go for a walk?]

757
00:45:41,340 --> 00:45:43,270
[Park Jae Ha: Do you want to rest?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: A walk? Suddenly?]

758
00:45:43,270 --> 00:45:46,270
[Park Jae Ha: Your blood sugar will spike
if you lie down after eating.]

759
00:45:47,810 --> 00:45:49,050
[Swoosh]

760
00:46:02,130 --> 00:46:04,610
[Park Jae Ha: You don't want to?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why are you suddenly here?]

761
00:46:04,610 --> 00:46:06,630
[Park Jae Ha: Hmm?]

762
00:46:06,630 --> 00:46:09,120
[Park Jae Ha: Is it sudden?]

763
00:46:10,870 --> 00:46:12,600
[Park Jae Ha: Want to go to Block A?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Hmm?]

764
00:46:12,600 --> 00:46:16,800
[Park Jae Ha: Shall we go there?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: What for?]

765
00:46:16,800 --> 00:46:21,230
[Park Jae Ha: I have a lot to tell you.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: OK.]

766
00:46:22,770 --> 00:46:27,060
[Park Jae Ha: It's cold outside. Dress warmly.]

767
00:46:31,610 --> 00:46:32,760
[A glance]

768
00:46:35,940 --> 00:46:37,720
[Reading the room]

769
00:46:37,720 --> 00:46:40,790
[All attention on Jae Ha and Hyeong Jun]

770
00:46:50,050 --> 00:46:53,920
[Park Jae Ha: He seems to have
misunderstood me in some ways.]

771
00:46:53,920 --> 00:46:58,710
[Park Jae Ha:
So I want to clear things up face to face,]

772
00:46:58,710 --> 00:47:02,070
[Park Jae Ha: somewhere no one is around.]

773
00:47:02,070 --> 00:47:05,390
[Park Jae Ha:
Block A has a game console room]

774
00:47:05,390 --> 00:47:09,060
[Park Jae Ha: with a hidden space inside.]

775
00:47:09,060 --> 00:47:12,640
[Park Jae Ha: So we went in to talk.]

776
00:47:13,050 --> 00:47:15,350
[Jae Ha's hard-earned chance for a conversation]

777
00:47:15,350 --> 00:47:20,240
[Park Jae Ha: We haven't had the chance]

778
00:47:20,240 --> 00:47:22,660
[Park Jae Ha: to have a proper chat, right?]

779
00:47:23,000 --> 00:47:25,080
[Park Jae Ha: No?]

780
00:47:25,080 --> 00:47:28,580
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I don't know what to say.]

781
00:47:30,800 --> 00:47:34,850
[Park Jae Ha:
If you told me not to do the reshoot,]

782
00:47:34,850 --> 00:47:37,640
[Park Jae Ha: I think I would've listened to you.]

783
00:47:37,640 --> 00:47:41,570
[Park Jae Ha: I don't think we talked...]

784
00:47:41,570 --> 00:47:45,040
[Park Jae Ha: about that properly.]

785
00:47:45,040 --> 00:47:50,570
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
This contradicts what you said in the car,]

786
00:47:50,570 --> 00:47:54,820
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
that even if I don't do the reshoot,]

787
00:47:54,820 --> 00:47:57,830
[Lee Hyeong Jun: you'd still want to do it,]

788
00:47:57,830 --> 00:48:00,240
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
that it matters more than our relationship.]

789
00:48:00,240 --> 00:48:02,960
[Lee Hyeong Jun: That's what you said.]

790
00:48:02,960 --> 00:48:06,040
[Park Jae Ha: About that...]

791
00:48:06,040 --> 00:48:10,400
[Park Jae Ha:
That's why I felt we really need to talk.]

792
00:48:11,630 --> 00:48:16,990
[Lee Hyeong Jun: But you were so sure then.]

793
00:48:16,990 --> 00:48:19,770
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Nothing can be changed now.]

794
00:48:30,430 --> 00:48:37,640
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I said I understood his stance,]

795
00:48:37,640 --> 00:48:41,310
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
but I've been struggling since the breakup.]

796
00:48:46,950 --> 00:48:53,620
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I told him I had a tough time]

797
00:48:53,620 --> 00:48:56,440
[Lee Hyeong Jun: and I was really hurt.]

798
00:48:59,670 --> 00:49:04,610
[Park Jae Ha: It's not because I like you less.]

799
00:49:04,610 --> 00:49:09,250
[Park Jae Ha: It's about the...
should I say, feelings and excitement]

800
00:49:09,250 --> 00:49:12,230
[Park Jae Ha:
about coming out to everyone I know.]

801
00:49:12,230 --> 00:49:16,200
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I know what you mean,]

802
00:49:16,200 --> 00:49:19,970
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
but regardless of your desire to come out,]

803
00:49:19,970 --> 00:49:23,890
[Lee Hyeong Jun: this is a dating show where you]

804
00:49:23,890 --> 00:49:27,280
[Lee Hyeong Jun: meet people to find love.]

805
00:49:27,280 --> 00:49:30,790
[Lee Hyeong Jun: So for me,]

806
00:49:30,790 --> 00:49:34,890
[Lee Hyeong Jun: it's a situation
where it was inevitable that I got really hurt.]

807
00:49:34,890 --> 00:49:40,700
[Lee Hyeong Jun: We didn't
meet or contact each other for over two weeks]

808
00:49:40,700 --> 00:49:42,960
[Lee Hyeong Jun: after that incident,]

809
00:49:42,960 --> 00:49:46,100
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
and I didn't really think about it.]

810
00:49:46,100 --> 00:49:50,330
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
Naturally, out of sight, out of mind.]

811
00:49:50,990 --> 00:49:53,100
[Lee Hyeong Jun: But it bothered me yesterday.]

812
00:49:53,100 --> 00:49:55,680
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
It felt like you were staring at me.]

813
00:49:55,680 --> 00:49:58,270
[Park Jae Ha: So you were avoiding my gaze.]

814
00:49:59,820 --> 00:50:01,400
[Park Jae Ha: I wanted to look you in the eyes,]

815
00:50:01,400 --> 00:50:03,720
[Park Jae Ha: but you never looked at me once.]

816
00:50:03,720 --> 00:50:06,360
[Lee Hyeong Jun: It was uncomfortable for me.]

817
00:50:14,710 --> 00:50:17,870
[Park Jae Ha: I guess I was too selfish.]

818
00:50:22,740 --> 00:50:24,610
[Park Jae Ha: Are you crying?]

819
00:50:26,260 --> 00:50:31,590
[Park Jae Ha: I'm sorry.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Don't come over.]

820
00:50:35,400 --> 00:50:38,840
[Park Jae Ha:
After listening to Hyeong Jun, if he were]

821
00:50:38,840 --> 00:50:40,460
[Park Jae Ha: in a calmer state,]

822
00:50:40,460 --> 00:50:42,880
[Park Jae Ha: I wouldn't be so hasty.]

823
00:50:42,880 --> 00:50:48,280
[Park Jae Ha: But his answers worried me more,]

824
00:50:48,280 --> 00:50:50,000
[Park Jae Ha: and I felt more guilty.]

825
00:50:51,440 --> 00:50:55,700
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I've said everything I want to.]

826
00:50:55,700 --> 00:51:00,790
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Before getting off the car then,
I'd said everything I wanted to.]

827
00:51:00,790 --> 00:51:02,940
[Lee Hyeong Jun: What I've just told you]

828
00:51:02,940 --> 00:51:07,900
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
were the reasons why I was upset and hurt.]

829
00:51:07,900 --> 00:51:11,670
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
I think I have nothing left to say.]

830
00:51:11,670 --> 00:51:16,900
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
I said everything I wanted to honestly.]

831
00:51:16,900 --> 00:51:21,150
[Lee Hyeong Jun: There's nothing specifically
that I want to hear from him.]

832
00:51:21,150 --> 00:51:24,740
[Park Jae Ha: In this week,
I'll try to clear up the misunderstandings]

833
00:51:24,740 --> 00:51:27,020
[Park Jae Ha: and express my sincerity.]

834
00:51:27,020 --> 00:51:30,930
[Park Jae Ha: Whatever's upsetting Hyeong Jun,]

835
00:51:30,930 --> 00:51:33,200
[Park Jae Ha: I'll work hard to fix it.]

836
00:51:33,820 --> 00:51:38,850
[Will Jae Ha's sincerity
reach Hyeong Jun's heart?]

837
00:51:54,630 --> 00:51:56,630
[There's no one, I think.]

838
00:51:56,750 --> 00:51:57,940
[(Come upstairs)]

839
00:51:57,940 --> 00:51:58,570
Who?

840
00:51:58,570 --> 00:51:59,210
[Beckoning]

841
00:51:59,210 --> 00:52:00,210
Oh.

842
00:52:00,760 --> 00:52:01,770
Oh.

843
00:52:10,360 --> 00:52:11,910
[Staring]

844
00:52:12,090 --> 00:52:14,360
[Cho Yun Jae: What are they... they...]
[Kim Su Min: Hmm?]

845
00:52:14,360 --> 00:52:16,490
[Cho Yun Jae: Where did he go?]

846
00:52:17,310 --> 00:52:19,600
[Cho Yun Jae: Whatever. What am I saying?]
[Kim Su Min: What is it?]

847
00:52:19,600 --> 00:52:21,710
[Cho Yun Jae: I don't know.]
[Kim Su Min: Now?]

848
00:52:21,710 --> 00:52:23,070
[Cho Yun Jae: Sorry?]
[Kim Su Min: What is it?]

849
00:52:23,070 --> 00:52:26,850
[Cho Yun Jae:
I don't know. Is there anything fun?]

850
00:52:27,580 --> 00:52:29,810
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Why are you so oblivious?]

851
00:52:29,810 --> 00:52:31,900
[Lee Hyun Jun: I thought you were asking about]

852
00:52:31,900 --> 00:52:33,470
[Lee Hyun Jun: people talking upstairs.]

853
00:52:33,470 --> 00:52:36,750
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Wow. "There's no one, I think"?]

854
00:52:36,750 --> 00:52:38,540
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Did anyone ask you out on a date?]

855
00:52:38,540 --> 00:52:39,930
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Besides me?]

856
00:52:39,930 --> 00:52:42,820
[(Nods)] [There was?]

857
00:52:42,820 --> 00:52:44,010
[Ah...]

858
00:52:44,010 --> 00:52:49,530
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Am I late? Too slow?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's a secret.]

859
00:52:49,530 --> 00:52:51,270
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I see.]

860
00:52:55,920 --> 00:52:58,580
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I think I know who it was.]

861
00:53:01,550 --> 00:53:03,960
[Lee Hyun Jun: Who do you think it was?]

862
00:53:03,960 --> 00:53:05,890
[Lee Hyeok Jin: It's a secret.]

863
00:53:06,680 --> 00:53:09,120
[Lee Hyeok Jin: In the previous shoot,]

864
00:53:09,120 --> 00:53:11,890
[Lee Hyeok Jin: we didn't have a proper date.]

865
00:53:11,890 --> 00:53:13,580
[Lee Hyeok Jin: You and I.]

866
00:53:14,990 --> 00:53:18,430
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
Does that guy want a date with you today too?]

867
00:53:18,430 --> 00:53:20,690
[Lee Hyun Jun: He didn't say when.]

868
00:53:20,690 --> 00:53:25,240
[Lee Hyun Jun: Just that he... wants a date.]

869
00:53:25,990 --> 00:53:31,360
[Lee Hyeok Jin: If we can date freely today,]

870
00:53:31,360 --> 00:53:34,430
[Lee Hyeok Jin: and you can pick your date,]

871
00:53:34,430 --> 00:53:37,200
[Lee Hyeok Jin: who'd you pick?]

872
00:53:37,200 --> 00:53:39,980
[Lee Hyun Jun: I get to pick?]

873
00:53:39,980 --> 00:53:42,030
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Well, yeah.]

874
00:53:43,430 --> 00:53:45,840
[Lee Hyun Jun: I haven't thought that far.]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Is it a secret?]

875
00:53:45,840 --> 00:53:49,170
[Lee Hyeok Jin: You haven't thought about it?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah, I haven't.]

876
00:53:49,170 --> 00:53:50,560
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I won't be as persistent]

877
00:53:50,560 --> 00:53:51,950
[Lee Hyeok Jin: as I was the last time.]

878
00:53:51,950 --> 00:53:54,210
[Lee Hyeok Jin: If anytime you feel that]

879
00:53:54,210 --> 00:53:56,480
[Lee Hyeok Jin: this isn't it,]

880
00:53:56,480 --> 00:53:59,090
[Lee Hyeok Jin: that there are zero sparks,]

881
00:53:59,090 --> 00:54:01,220
[Lee Hyeok Jin: that it won't work out]

882
00:54:01,220 --> 00:54:03,360
[Lee Hyeok Jin: no matter what I do,]

883
00:54:03,360 --> 00:54:07,740
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I hope you can be direct with me.
I won't feel hurt.]

884
00:54:07,740 --> 00:54:10,600
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's not easy to be that direct.]

885
00:54:10,600 --> 00:54:12,630
[Lee Hyun Jun: It'll weigh on me.]

886
00:54:12,630 --> 00:54:15,410
[Lee Hyeok Jin: That's true.]

887
00:54:16,350 --> 00:54:19,370
[Lee Hyeok Jin: That's all I want to say today.]

888
00:54:19,370 --> 00:54:22,690
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I thought I should let you know.]

889
00:54:22,690 --> 00:54:24,570
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah.]

890
00:54:25,350 --> 00:54:27,840
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
I'll call you out like this often.]

891
00:54:27,840 --> 00:54:29,570
[Lee Hyun Jun: OK.]

892
00:54:29,570 --> 00:54:30,930
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Keep an eye out for me.]

893
00:54:30,930 --> 00:54:33,470
[Lee Hyun Jun: Got it.]

894
00:54:34,340 --> 00:54:37,320
[Lee Hyeok Jin: His reaction was pretty good,]

895
00:54:37,320 --> 00:54:38,990
[Lee Hyeok Jin: but you know,]

896
00:54:39,000 --> 00:54:42,300
[Lee Hyeok Jin: that's how Hyun Jun always reacts.]

897
00:54:42,600 --> 00:54:45,240
[Lee Hyeok Jin: But I still want to try again.]

898
00:54:45,240 --> 00:54:48,630
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I want to do whatever I can]

899
00:54:48,630 --> 00:54:52,690
[Lee Hyeok Jin: and go for it again.]

900
00:54:53,480 --> 00:54:55,010
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Last game before we go?]

901
00:54:55,360 --> 00:54:56,290
[Swoosh]

902
00:54:56,420 --> 00:54:58,890
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I'm great at the Halli Galli game.]

903
00:54:58,890 --> 00:55:00,300
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You know the version]

904
00:55:00,300 --> 00:55:01,240
[Eum Hyeok Jin: where you grab one ear?]

905
00:55:01,240 --> 00:55:02,750
I've played it before.

906
00:55:02,750 --> 00:55:05,080
I almost ripped my ear once.

907
00:55:05,530 --> 00:55:07,740
[A glance]

908
00:55:12,570 --> 00:55:14,480
[Eum Hyeok Jin: (whispers)
Want to go for a walk if there's time later?]

909
00:55:14,480 --> 00:55:16,360
[Kim Han Gyeol: OK.]

910
00:55:19,720 --> 00:55:22,360
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Half each, right?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes.]

911
00:55:22,360 --> 00:55:27,410
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I've been waiting
for a chance to say that to him.]

912
00:55:27,410 --> 00:55:29,300
[Eum Hyeok Jin: If others were around,]

913
00:55:29,300 --> 00:55:31,490
[Eum Hyeok Jin: he might feel pressured,]

914
00:55:32,210 --> 00:55:34,970
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
and I didn't want anyone to know either.]

915
00:55:34,970 --> 00:55:37,870
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I said it
when it was just the two of us.]

916
00:55:37,870 --> 00:55:41,120
[Eum Hyeok Jin: To be honest,
it's my first time being so forward,]

917
00:55:41,120 --> 00:55:44,860
[Eum Hyeok Jin: so I was a little nervous.]

918
00:55:44,860 --> 00:55:48,020
[Kim Han Gyeol: Eum Hyeok Jin's been asking
if I wanted to go for a walk.]

919
00:55:48,020 --> 00:55:51,830
[Kim Han Gyeol:
He has started to be more forward with me.]

920
00:55:51,830 --> 00:55:54,170
[Kim Han Gyeol: I don't dislike his flirting.]

921
00:55:54,170 --> 00:55:57,640
[Kim Han Gyeol: I quite like it.]

922
00:56:03,530 --> 00:56:06,600
[Someone is approaching Men's House]

923
00:56:10,490 --> 00:56:14,310
[A mystery man is here to stir up hearts]

924
00:56:14,430 --> 00:56:15,530
It's so hard.

925
00:56:23,790 --> 00:56:26,350
[A new participant arrives when they least expect]

926
00:56:26,570 --> 00:56:30,030
[How will he shake things up?]

927
00:56:30,590 --> 00:56:32,870
[The calm before the storm]

928
00:56:36,920 --> 00:56:40,680
[Here comes a new man]

929
00:57:00,090 --> 00:57:07,620
[The guy who has shown up at Men's House is...]
